import React, { Component } from "react"
import Navbar from "./Navbar"
import Input from "./Input"
import { Wrap, TextContainer, Text, SubText, Line } from "./styles/header"

class Header extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Wrap>
        <Navbar />
        <TextContainer>
          <Text>
            Ready for A <Line>Holiday</Line>?
          </Text>
          <SubText> CHECK OUT OUR LATEST PROMOTION </SubText>
          <Input />
        </TextContainer>
      </Wrap>
    )
  }
}

export default Header
